"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1823a6bdc51230bbb5691a0a2bd5547865398620","tid":2216105,"uid":152790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"400呎唔駛買2000蚊router啦<br />\n我有隻86u 冇用<br />\n比你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779029ab2d7ac8aae34161df22dbe8fb60cdf19f","tid":2216105,"uid":335003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"首先插lan 線一定用得盡 1Gb <br />\n<br />\n無線首先每條天線理論值同現實大概差一半。<br />\nac (wifi5) 開始單枝天線理論值 (5Ghz) 200Mbs(40Mhz)/<br />\n433Mbs(80Mhz)/<br />\n866Mbs(160Mhz)<br />\n<br />\n新嘅單枝通常866，你 router 夠天線可以同時射幾條 866 channel 俾你，但如果你部機無咁多條天線咁你最多都淨係收到你部機接收天線上限嘅速度。<br />\n<br />\n你收signal 部機單天線就得  866，雙天線就 1732 etc. <br />\n然後實速再對半， 所以想用盡1Ghz 最少接收果部機都要有3條866嘅天線。如果部機無咁新，433天線就要有 5 -6 條。 <br />\n而啲 mobile device 空間有限，通常都係裝2條5Ghz 天線左右。平嘅得1條唔奇、再入門級可能得 2.4Ghz 天線，無5Ghz 天線。<br />\n<br />\nwifi 6 強化咗對多部使用wifi 嘅 device 支援，減少延遲。 如果你得一部二部機用 wifi ，咁 wifi 5&amp;6 分別不大。  不過香港人屋企閒閒哋都4、5部 嘢一齊用wifi， 每條/組天線要同時對幾部機就直接買 wifi 6 有著數。<br />\n<br />\n所以你就算買完，未必部部機都會行得盡 1Gbs，不過正常部 router 應該會出得足俾你。<br />\n<br />\n唔計強國啲無牌子19 router 夠天線，不過router 入面用垃圾 chips 等硬件支援唔到同時咁多條線。"},{"pid":"f67c33594de1b6a286dd7615099229d99d3491f4","tid":2216105,"uid":190715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d450f8c18a6352d13892a9566dc9faad92f5ba7e","tid":2216105,"uid":308964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:19:14.000Z","msg":"hi 各位ching好<br />\n小弟未買過router<br />\n所以想上黎請教下各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\